alerts.text:
Tuesday 4 to Thursday 6 October
Nightly from 9.40pm until 1am

City Circle
- Trains run in one direction only, from Central first stop Museum.

T2 Airport Line
- Trains from the City start from Central.

T2 Inner West & South Line
- Some trains from the City end at Central.

You may need to change trains to complete your journey if travelling to or from City Circle stations.
